<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title>{{ invoice.filename }}</title>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ absolute_url(asset("build/app.css")) }}">
    </head>
    <body>
        <page class="page">
            <div class="invoice-pdf">
                <div class="pdf-header">
                    <h2 class="-title">{{ invoice.filename }}</h2>
                    <p>Date d'émission : {{ invoice.invoiceDate|date("d/m/Y") }}</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="pdf-client">
                    <table class="table">
                        <thead>
                            <tr>
                                <th class="w-50">Prestataire</th>
                                <th class="w-50">Client</th>
                            </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody>
                            <tr>
                                <td class="-freelance">
                                    {% set user = invoice.user %}
                                    <div class="service-provider">
                                        <div class="-identity">
                                            <span class="txt-bold">{{ user.fullname }}</span>
                                        </div>
                                        
                                        {% if user.freelance is not same as (null) %}
                                            <div class="-address">
                                                <span>{{ user.freelance.address ~ ", " ~ user.freelance.zipCode ~ " " ~ user.freelance.city ~ ", " ~ user.freelance.country }}</span>
                                            </div>
                                        {% endif %}
                                        
                                        <div class="-contact">
                                            {% if user.freelance is not same as (null) %}<span>{{ user.freelance.phone }}</span><br />{% endif %}
                                            <span>{{ user.email }}</span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </td>
                                <td class="-client">
                                    {% set company = invoice.company %}
                                    <div class="service-provider">
                                        <div class="-identity">
                                            <span class="txt-bold">{{ company.name }}</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="-address">
                                            <span>{{ company.address ~ ", " ~ company.zipCode ~ " " ~ company.city ~ ", " ~ company.country }}</span><br />
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="-contact">
                                            {% if company.phone %}<span>{{ company.phone }}</span><br />{% endif %}
                                            {% if company.email %}<span>{{ company.email }}</span>{% endif %}
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>
                
                <div class="pdf-body">
                    <div class="w-100">
                        <table class="table">
                            <thead>
                                <tr>
                                    <th class="column-description">Description</th>
                                    <th class="column-quantity">Quantity</th>
                                    <th class="column-price">Price</th>
                                    <th class="column-tva">TVA</th>
                                    <th class="column-amount">Amount</th>
                                </tr>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody>
                                {% for invoiceDetail in invoice.invoiceDetails %}
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="-description txt-left">{{ invoiceDetail.description }}</td>
                                        <td class="-quantity txt-center">{{ invoiceDetail.quantity }}</td>
                                        <td class="-price txt-center">{{ invoiceDetail.price }}</td>
                                        <td class="-tya txt-center">{{ invoiceDetail.tva ? "Yes" : "No" }}</td>
                                        <td class="-amount txt-center">{{ (invoiceDetail.price * invoiceDetail.quantity) * (invoiceDetail.tva ? 1.2 : 1) }}</td>
                                    </tr>
                                {% endfor %}
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="mt-25px w-50 f-left"></div>
                    
                    <div class="mt-25px w-50 f-right">
                        <table class="table">
                            <tbody>
                                <tr>
                                    <td class="-m-hidden">Sub total</td>
                                    <td class="-amount">{{ invoice.getAmount() }}</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td class="-m-hidden">TVA (20%)</td>
                                    <td class="-tva">{{ invoice.getTvaAmount() }}</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr class="txt-bold">
                                    <td class="-m-hidden">Total</td>
                                    <td class="-total">{{ invoice.getTotalAmount() }}</td>
                                </tr>
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="pdf-footer">
                    <p>
                        La loi n°92/1442 du 31 décembre 1992 nous fait l’obligation de vous indiquer que le non-respect des conditions de paiement entraîne des intérêts de retard suivant modalités et taux définis par la loi. Une indemnité forfaitaire de 40€ sera due pour frais de recouvrement en cas de retard de paiement.<br /><br />
                        Mode de règlement : Virement ou chèque<br /><br />
                        Date limite de règlement : 30 jours
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </page>
    </body>
</html>